{"title":"「CQOI2016」K 远点对","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":["2016","CQOI","k-d Tree","数据结构"],"operation":{"submit":"https://loj.ac/problem/2043#submit_code","submissions":"https://loj.ac/submissions?problem_id=2043","statistics":"https://loj.ac/problem/2043/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://loj.ac/problem/2043/testdata","discussion":"https://loj.ac/discussion/problem/2043"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"已知平面内 $N$ 个点的坐标，求欧氏距离下的第 $K$ 远点对。\r\n\r\n两个点 $P(x_1, y_1)$ 和 $Q(x_2, y_2)$ 的欧氏距离定义为 $d(P, Q) = \\sqrt {(x_1 - x_2)^2 + (y_1 - y_2)^2}$。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入文件第一行为用空格隔开的两个整数 $N, K$。  \r\n接下来 $N$ 行，每行两个整数 $X, Y$，表示一个点的坐标。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出文件第一行为一个整数，表示第 $K$ 远点对的距离的平方（一定是个整数）。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入\r\n```plain\r\n10 5\r\n0 0\r\n0 1\r\n1 0\r\n1 1\r\n2 0\r\n2 1\r\n1 2\r\n0 2\r\n3 0\r\n3 1\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出\r\n```plain\r\n9\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"| Case # | $N$ |\r\n|:---:|:---:|\r\n| 1 | $2000$ |\r\n| 2 | $5000$ |\r\n| 3 | $10000$ |\r\n| 4 | $15000$ |\r\n| 5 | $20000$ |\r\n| 6 | $60000$ |\r\n| 7 | $70000$ |\r\n| 8 | $80000$ |\r\n| 9 | $90000$ |\r\n| 10 | $100000$ |\r\n\r\n对于所有测试点，$1 \\leq K \\leq 100, K \\leq \\frac {N(N-1)} {2}, 0 \\leq X, Y \\lt 2^{31}$。"}]}